Text.Value: |Eated! Eated! Is it eated or eaten, sis?|
|We generally eat people and other animals that end up here|
|But wait! Goblins are so much tastier and with our animal forces combined, we can get a feast unlike anything you had!|
|But the cage gate is closed and we cannot leave right now. Open it and feast shall be ours|
|But why tho? We can have a feast right here right now. Again, prepare to get eated.|
|You must be new here. Care for a tour of our place?|
|At least you recognize us as animals. Refreshing!|
|*Spiders scurry away towards the open cage gate*|
|We should attack goblins! They are tasty!|
